{"tid":2429093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"盼「撞鬼」轉運毁150金塔 兩青年判社服令 母自責教不好 官安慰","createTime":"2021-03-02T05:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T07:30:00.000Z","uid":80481,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b77e54e1bd0a4cedfff7424e347440842f7fa574","tid":2429093,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:12:02.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】兩名分別任職跟車工人和倉務員的青年，聲稱一時貪玩，誤以為「撞鬼」能帶來好運，趁夜深到天水圍民德路後山，用鐵棍毁壞150個載有附近3條村原居民先人骸骨的金塔，其中一人更在金塔上小便。二人早前承認刑事毁壞罪，昨日被判240小時社會服務令。<br />\n官：清明節村民點去拜祭？<br />\n被告林嘉樂及邵俊偉（均20歲），各自呈上3份求情信，其中由其母親撰寫的求情信皆指自己管教不好，邵的母親更自稱為「失敗的母親」。兩被告皆在求情信中稱對於犯案令家人受傷害感到內疚，望法庭給予機會。<br />\n裁判官判刑時稱，兩被告同樣由母親獨力照顧，二人母親對兒子干犯罪行都非常自責，甚至責怪自己貧窮。裁判官認為被告母親不應自責，指兩被告已是成年人，應明白需要尊重先人，尤其邵父已經過身，應明白後人對先人的懷念，質問兩名被告：「噚日（周一）清明節，村民點去拜祭？」<br />\n裁判官警告兩被告，若未能完成社會服務令，有可能被判入勞教中心。控方原要求法庭下令兩名被告賠償約33萬元，惟裁判官指被告沒有經濟能力支付，終未有頒下賠償令。"},{"pid":"c639ae2b62f24f57d579ad9474c3b8b55ed39d10","tid":2429093,"uid":80481,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"想知呢兩個被告過左咁多年之後有冇撞鬼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f582f9162fb519288275271771c21b245adc151","tid":2429093,"uid":59898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"唔怕原居民斬7佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被人斬唔方唔轉運"},{"pid":"eb24965d0654d8fb305b3f34cbb2e983fd124527","tid":2429093,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"曾經有諗過靠撞鬼 學念能力"},{"pid":"fb269e380fe2910e2da7b2c9015782c2669bb7c8","tid":2429093,"uid":5502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:12:34.000Z","msg":"話學文革破四舊立四新，應該即放"},{"pid":"205029a6f6cfca23d478da03c285318ddc9963ea","tid":2429093,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"可能想 屌女鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a2c241a962d441461d1151d7c23182f558655f","tid":2429093,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:17:47.000Z","msg":"咁都未比人斬 已經好好運"},{"pid":"6bd65fc762560dc304f80ee4d096e64cd24c73eb","tid":2429093,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:19:35.000Z","msg":"噚日清明？"},{"pid":"613258bd7544e210c00851c1746d84ddc36d0b43","tid":2429093,"uid":121813,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7Shmhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7Shmhf.jpg&h=66b87744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb62b98dbe433b76835af6a508721ebba412367","tid":2429093,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"兩個都單親家庭...佢地肯定好好兄弟"},{"pid":"e18d4adc73dae1cdbd4c9ad878ac87353060c213","tid":2429093,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:30:00.000Z","msg":"2016年4月6日"}]}